Formatting Tag
--------------
<b>             boldness
<i>             italic
<u>             underline

<strong>        bold (html5)
<em>            italic (html5)

<big>           font size > normal size
<small>         font size < normal size

<sup>           in power
<sub>           in base

<mark>          higlight text 
<strike>        line through (deprecated)
<q>             double quotes
<del>           line through
<blockquote>    indentation
<center>        align content in center

Heading Tag
|- <h1> 32 px (pixel = picture element)
|- <h2> 24 px
|- <h3> 19 px 
|- <h4> 16 px default font size
|- <h5> 13 px
|- <h6> 11 px

<marquee>       for moving text 
<code>          something needs to write in code form 
<pre>           pre formatted tag
<address>       italic  
<font color="" face="">
    here face means font family    
